OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sat 25 Jul to Mon 3 Aug
OL,6,FThis period looks like being largely
OL,7,Fchangeable, with many parts likely to
OL,8,Fsee some rain at times. Rain will
OL,9,Fspread southeast across most if not
OL,10,Fall parts of the UK through this
OL,11,Fweekend, with some showers following.
OL,12,FFurther bands of rain look likely to
OL,13,Fspread southeast next week,
OL,14,Finterspersed with sunny spells and
OL,15,Fsome showers. Confidence becomes lower
OL,16,Fas we approach the turn of the month,
OL,17,Fbut there are hints that high pressure
OL,18,Fcould return for a time, which would
OL,19,Fmean dry conditions resuming,
OL,20,Fespecially in the south. Winds will be
OL,21,Fmostly light or moderate, but
OL,22,Foccasionally fresh or strong around
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,23,Fsome coasts, mainly in the north.
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
OL,24,FTemperatures will be near or above
OL,25,Fnormal, warmest in the south, and
OL,26,Fperhaps becoming very warm again by
FL,164,160,301,260,100,100
